	<h3>Activation Context (2)</h3>
	
	Look at the URL of this page. 
	It is the page render request from the PageLink, and the <strong>activation context</strong> is at the end.<br/><br/>
	
	This page handles the <em>activate</em> event by providing a method like this:<br/><br/>
	
	<pre><code>
	void onActivate(Long personId) {
		this.personId = personId;
	}
	</code></pre><br/>
	
	The method receives the activation context into <code>personId</code>. Its value is <em>${personId}</em>. Here is that Person:<br/>

